{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmailTags:forEmail:","role":"symbol","title":"setEmailTags:forEmail:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmailTags:forEmail:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmailTags:forEmail:","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmailTags:forEmail:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemailtags:foremail:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmailTags:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tags"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"forEmail:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"email","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to associate with the email.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray, NSNull (to delete)."}]}],"name":"tags"},{"name":"email","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The email address to associate tags with. Must be a valid email format.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates tags with an email address independently of the current device."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is used for email-specific segmentation in Pushwoosh Email campaigns.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Email tags are separate from device tags:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Device tags: Associated with push token, used for push segmentation"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Email tags: Associated with email address, used for email segmentation"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this for email-specific attributes like email preferences, engagement metrics,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"or email-only campaign targeting.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update email campaign preferences:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class EmailPreferencesManager {","","    func updateEmailPreferences(for email: String, preferences: EmailPreferences) {","        let tags: [String: Any] = [","            \"email_frequency\": preferences.frequency.rawValue,","            \"email_categories\": preferences.subscribedCategories.map { $0.rawValue },","            \"email_format\": preferences.preferHTML ? \"html\" : \"plain\",","            \"unsubscribed_categories\": preferences.unsubscribedCategories.map { $0.rawValue },","            \"last_preference_update\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date())","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmailTags(tags, forEmail: email)","    }","","    func trackEmailEngagement(email: String, campaignId: String, action: EmailAction) {","        l